{"tid":1829262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［代Post］沒有林卓廷 沒有721","createTime":"2020-01-18T14:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T15:35:19.000Z","uid":246340,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a896d2e6197d90a69a6edffdfcde6e45592a7d52","tid":1829262,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T14:43:00.000Z","msg":"第一次開po 屌得細力啲<br />\n<br />\n721警黑勾結一直都係班狗既大死穴 班狗係點都駁唔到 <br />\n有曬片 前排咁抵死班豬隊友仲可以講得出 沒有林卓廷 沒有721 咁蠢既野 <br />\n<br />\n與其向班藍絲澄清 不如將計就計 重新將721既輿論去返之前既熱門 <br />\n到時班藍絲都討論番721一定要查清楚林卓廷條仆街<br />\n<br />\n點知查兩查....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以文宣方向可唔可以 照返藍絲口味 ：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">721 幕後黑手林....../這個人一手造成721禍局<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d9f2f623da80460a39926beb4ef4549983b0d07a","tid":1829262,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有林卓廷 沒有721<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"2c8a09de0984bfd5ea54a10af7461bfe0337d97a","tid":1829262,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T14:43:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有林卓廷 沒有721<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"4e429467f9453606ba141f82cc5210984b83506d","tid":1829262,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有林卓廷 沒有721<br />\n</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"0a4355f5719c43917970fb18110ae3275b356814","tid":1829262,"uid":246340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"<